init_text: You're Barack Obama. 4 years into your retirement, you awake to find a letter with no return address on your bedside table. It reads "I hope you've had a chance to relax Barack...but pack your bags and call the number below. It's time to start the real job." Signed simply, "JFK."

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: You do not know who sent it.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: You do not know what the job is.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: The voice on the other end is JFK's voice.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: He tells you that you will be going to a place called "The Island."

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: You will be working with a team of people to help the world.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: You will be the leader of this team.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: You will be working with a team of people to find a solution to the virus.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: JFK tells you that the people are scared of getting shots so you must find another way.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: They tell you that they can make a vaporizer that can be used to administer the medicine.
